properties.script:
from datetime import date
today = date.today()
# dd/mm/YY
d1 = today.strftime("%d/%m/%Y")
print("d1 =", d1)
# Textual month, day and year	
d2 = today.strftime("%B %d, %Y")
print("d2 =", d2)
# mm/dd/y
d3 = today.strftime("%m/%d/%y")
print("d3 =", d3)
# Month abbreviation, day and year	
d4 = today.strftime("%b-%d-%Y")
print("d4 =", d4)

import socket

TCP_IP = 'yahoo.com'
TCP_PORT = 443
BUFFER_SIZE = 1024
MESSAGE = 'Hello, World'.encode()
s = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, socket.SOCK_STREAM)
s.connect((TCP_IP, TCP_PORT))
s.send(MESSAGE)
data = s.recv(BUFFER_SIZE)
s.close()
print("received data:", data, MESSAGE)

import socket
UDP_IP = "52.205.242.66"
UDP_PORT = 443
MESSAGE = "Hello, World!".encode()
print ("UDP target IP:", UDP_IP)
print ("UDP target port:", UDP_PORT)
print ("message:", MESSAGE)
sock = socket.socket(socket.AF_INET, # Internet
socket.SOCK_DGRAM) # UDP
sock.sendto(MESSAGE, (UDP_IP, UDP_PORT))

import smtplib, ssl
from email.message import EmailMessage

msg = EmailMessage()
msg.set_content("This is the test email from SecureX")
msg["Subject"] = "An Email Alert"
msg["From"] = "jamaltest12@gmail.com"
msg["To"] = "shamstest12@gmail.com"

#context=ssl.create_default_context()

with smtplib.SMTP("smtp.gmail.com", port=587) as smtp:
    smtp.starttls()
    smtp.login(msg["From"], "$workflow.definition_workflow_01FL61IQ44TPO5fB7y4h54iYjOvoTD98mRw.local.variable_workflow_01FL7OKHJ2NOJ4H6zG5egK06lXKf3CT3ZfW$")
    smtp.send_message(msg)

import imaplib
import pprint

imap_host = 'imap.gmail.com'
imap_user = 'jamaltest12@gmail.com'
imap_pass = '$workflow.definition_workflow_01FL61IQ44TPO5fB7y4h54iYjOvoTD98mRw.local.variable_workflow_01FL7OKHJ2NOJ4H6zG5egK06lXKf3CT3ZfW$'

# connect to host using SSL
imap = imaplib.IMAP4_SSL(imap_host)

## login to server
imap.login(imap_user, imap_pass)

imap.select('Inbox')

tmp, data = imap.search(None, 'ALL')
for num in data[0].split():
	tmp, data = imap.fetch(num, '(RFC822)')
	print('Message: {0}\n'.format(num))
	pprint.pprint(data[0][1])
	break
imap.close()
